## 22. ADVANCED SCROLL-DRIVEN MOTION SEQUENCES (GSAP + Lenis)

Detailed instructions for implementing multi-stage scroll storytelling:

### 22.1: Horizontal Showcase Scroll Setup
Coordinate horizontal panning container pinned relative to the viewport:
```javascript
export function initHorizontalScroll(containerSelector, triggerSelector) {
  const container = document.querySelector(containerSelector);
  const trigger = document.querySelector(triggerSelector);
  
  const scrollWidth = container.scrollWidth - window.innerWidth;
  
  gsap.to(container, {
    x: -scrollWidth,
    ease: "none",
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: trigger,
      pin: true,
      scrub: 1,
      start: "top top",
      end: () => `+=${scrollWidth}`,
      invalidateOnRefresh: true
    }
  });
}
```

### 22.2: Sticky Narrative Layout
* Pin copy cards on the left viewport column while images scroll on the right.
* Unpin only when the last slide reaches a scroll offset of `90%` viewport height.

