## 24. WORKSPACE DIRECTORY & FILE MAPPING PROTOCOL

All systems load dependencies in order. Reference the manifest below to coordinate module imports:
* `DESIGN_OS` -> Core token stylesheet definitions.
* `MOTION_SYSTEM` -> Animation physics properties. Requires `DESIGN_OS` to be parsed first.
* `CREATIVE_TECH_SYSTEM` -> WebGL canvases and Rapier WASM bindings. Requires `MOTION_SYSTEM`.
* `STORYTELLING_SYSTEM` -> Narrative layouts and page routing structures. Requires `DESIGN_OS` and `TYPOGRAPHY_SYSTEM`.
